      <h1>Commercial Refrigerator Price & Buying Guide India 2026</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span>📅 Updated: March 2026</span>
        <span>⏱️ 13 min read</span>
        <span>🇮🇳 India-focused pricing</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Commercial refrigerator prices in India in 2026 range from ₹25,000 for a basic single-door reach-in refrigerator to ₹15 lakh or more for a large walk-in cold room.</strong> Choosing the right commercial refrigeration is critical — it protects your ingredients, ensures food safety compliance under FSSAI guidelines, and directly affects your operating costs. This guide covers every type of commercial refrigeration available in India, with honest pricing and buying advice.</p>

    <h2>Commercial Refrigerator Price List India 2026</h2>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Type</th><th>Capacity</th><th>Price Range (INR)</th><th>Best For</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Single-Door Reach-In Fridge</td><td>150–300 L</td><td>₹25,000 – ₹65,000</td><td>Small kitchens, cloud kitchens</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Double-Door Reach-In Fridge</td><td>400–600 L</td><td>₹55,000 – ₹1,20,000</td><td>Medium restaurants, bakeries</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Triple-Door Reach-In Fridge</td><td>700–900 L</td><td>₹1,00,000 – ₹2,00,000</td><td>Large restaurants, hotels</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Under-Counter Fridge</td><td>100–200 L</td><td>₹20,000 – ₹55,000</td><td>Bar areas, prep stations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Refrigerated Display Case</td><td>100–400 L</td><td>₹35,000 – ₹2,50,000</td><td>Bakeries, dessert shops</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Commercial Chest Freezer</td><td>200–700 L</td><td>₹20,000 – ₹90,000</td><td>Bulk frozen storage</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Upright Commercial Freezer</td><td>200–600 L</td><td>₹35,000 – ₹1,50,000</td><td>Easy-access frozen storage</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Blast Chiller (5-tray)</td><td>5 trays</td><td>₹1,20,000 – ₹2,50,000</td><td>Bake-off bakeries, HACCP compliance</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Walk-In Cold Room (small)</td><td>up to 10 m²</td><td>₹2,50,000 – ₹5,00,000</td><td>Medium bakeries, restaurants</td></tr>
